reviewText:
Run (?), Snail, Run!

It's about:life full of adventures;
long way home;
pixel-hunting;
solving puzzles.
Why you should play this:gameplay - it's a mix of puzzle and pixel hunting: by solving puzzles you pass through levels, hunting for stars you unlock Bob's additional costumes;
a lot of cheeky reference to different famous video-games, TV-series, movies.
Why you may not like it:it's easy and childish.
Your own limitless source of positive emotions.
